<doc>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_AUTOSCROLL_CONFIGURATION">
    <summary>
      <para>Determines the type and direction of automatic scrolling animation to apply.</para>
    </summary>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//previous-versions/windows/desktop/directmanipulation/direct-manipulation-enumerations">Direct Manipulation Enumerations</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_AUTOSCROLL_CONFIGURATION.DIRECTMANIPULATION_AUTOSCROLL_CONFIGURATION_STOP">
    <summary>
      <para>If content is scrolling, slowly stop along the direction of the motion.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_AUTOSCROLL_CONFIGURATION.DIRECTMANIPULATION_AUTOSCROLL_CONFIGURATION_FORWARD">
    <summary>
      <para>Scroll towards the positive boundary of the content.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_AUTOSCROLL_CONFIGURATION.DIRECTMANIPULATION_AUTOSCROLL_CONFIGURATION_REVERSE">
    <summary>
      <para>Scroll towards the origin of the content.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>